---
import ServiceLayout from '@layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Eco-Friendly Candle Making"
  description="Learn sustainable candle making with eco-friendly materials in Centerville, TN. Create beautiful, environmentally conscious candles."
  price="$25-35 per person"
  duration="2 hours"
  location="Centerville, TN"
  keywords="eco-friendly candles, sustainable candles, green crafting, Centerville"
>
  <section slot="overview">
    <h2>Eco-Friendly Candle Making - Centerville, TN</h2>
    <p>
      Create beautiful candles while making environmentally conscious choices. Our Eco-Friendly Candle Making workshop teaches sustainable techniques using natural, biodegradable materials that are better for your home and the planet.
    </p>

    <h3>The Experience</h3>
    <p>
      Learn how to make candles the sustainable way. We use 100% soy wax (renewable resource), natural fiber wicks, biodegradable packaging, and eco-friendly fragrance oils. You'll create gorgeous candles that are better for the environment without sacrificing quality or beauty.
    </p>

    <h3>What's Included</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Education on sustainable candle making</li>
      <li>100% soy wax (renewable and biodegradable)</li>
      <li>Natural fiber wicks</li>
      <li>Eco-friendly fragrance options</li>
      <li>Sustainable containers and packaging</li>
      <li>Professional pouring instruction</li>
      <li>Take home 2-3 eco-friendly candles</li>
      <li>Sustainability guide for your home</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Perfect For</h3>
    <p>
      Environmentally conscious individuals, sustainability advocates, and anyone seeking green lifestyle practices. Great for eco-conscious gift-giving.
    </p>

    <h3>Our Eco-Friendly Approach</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Soy wax: renewable, biodegradable resource</li>
      <li>Paper-tube wicks: natural fiber alternatives</li>
      <li>Eco fragrance oils: natural, sustainable sources</li>
      <li>Recyclable glass containers</li>
      <li>Compostable packaging materials</li>
      <li>Zero-waste process</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>How It Works</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>Sustainability education (10 minutes)</li>
      <li>Explore eco-friendly material options (10 minutes)</li>
      <li>Hands-on candle creation (50 minutes)</li>
      <li>Finishing and sustainable packaging (10 minutes)</li>
      <li>Take home your green candles!</li>
    </ol>

    <h3>Pricing & Duration</h3>
    <p>
      <strong>Price:</strong> $25-35 per person<br />
      <strong>Duration:</strong> 2 hours<br />
      <strong>Group Size:</strong> 1-6 people<br />
      <strong>Skill Level:</strong> All levels welcome
    </p>

    <div style="background: #e8f4f8; padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin: 2rem 0; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><strong>Make sustainable candles!</strong> Call (931) 729-8459 or email made@thelocalplacetn.com. Located at 111 South Public Square, Upstairs, Centerville, TN 37033.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section slot="testimonials">
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"Love that I can create beautiful candles AND help the environment! This was exactly what I was looking for!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Hannah L.</strong> - Nashville (45 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"As someone passionate about sustainability, this workshop was perfect. Candles that feel good to make!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Owen T.</strong> - Brentwood (40 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"My whole family is eco-conscious now. These candles are beautiful AND guilt-free!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Bianca J.</strong> - Franklin (35 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section slot="related">
    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem;">
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Candle Making Workshop</h3>
        <p>Learn professional candle-making techniques from start to finish.</p>
        <a href="/candle-store/candle-making-workshop" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Pour Your Own Candle Class</h3>
        <p>Create beautiful hand-poured candles with custom colors and scents.</p>
        <a href="/candle-store/pour-your-own-candle-class" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Essential Oil Candle Workshop</h3>
        <p>Create luxurious candles using pure essential oils.</p>
        <a href="/candle-store/essential-oil-candle-workshop" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
